milestones.description: Shaiman Anwar and Haider's 54-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 31 between Saleem Raza and Mohammad Aslam
Hamid Hassan has become the top wicket-taker for AFG in ODIs with 41 wickets, going past Samiullah Shinwari's 39
This is the lowest match aggregate (486) involving teams U.A.E. & Afghanistan in ODIs
Alhashmi has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for UAE, going past Shahzad's 2
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for AFG, going past Shapoor's 3
Samiullah Shinwari has scored 7 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for AFG breaking Mohammad Nabi's record
Mohammad Nabi has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (41) for AFG, going past Samiullah Shinwari

stories.title: All-round UAE clinch series 3-1
stories.subTitle: UAE v Afghanistan, 4th ODI, Dubai
stories.summary: Fifties from Andre Berenger and Shaiman Anwar, followed by three-wicket hauls from Kamran Shazad and Rohan Mustafa set up UAE's 30-run victory against Afghanistan in Dubai, enabling the team to take the series 3-1
